{
  "id": "acornPlansRenderer",
  "name": "Acorn Plans - Windows Renderer (review mode)",
  "active": false,
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Acorn Plans - Windows Renderer (Review Mode)\n\nCurrent production workflow. Calls the Windows `render_service.py` over HTTP, uploads every generated VSDX to SharePoint `General/AI Automation/AI_COMPLETED`, then marks the source email read and moves it to Outlook `AI_COMPLETED`.\n\nKeep the old `Automated Drawing` / `plangenration` workflow deactivated; it produces weaker `AI Draft` files and can consume emails before this workflow sees them.\n\nUses n8n env: `RENDER_SERVICE_URL`, `RENDER_SERVICE_TOKEN`. Do not hardcode the render token in workflow JSON.",
        "height": 320,
        "width": 520
      },
      "id": "note_review_mode",
      "name": "README",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        120,
        180
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "*/10 7-18 * * 1-5"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "schedule_business_hours",
      "name": "Every 10 min (business hrs)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [
        380,
        540
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "={{ ($env.RENDER_SERVICE_URL || 'http://16.61.179.204:8765') + '/ready' }}",
        "options": {
          "timeout": 8000
        }
      },
      "id": "wait_ready",
      "name": "Wait for /ready (poll until renderable)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        580,
        540
      ],
